Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't change even \Nwhen we blew the whistle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikaidar really got a lot of airtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that? We were telling \Nyou to change the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:16.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's with the next \Nepisode of {\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soujirou here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.41,0:23:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Sou-{\i1}kun{\i0}, I'll be going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't separate \Nmy spirit from my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure I can learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-{\i1}kun{\i0}, you're still talking \Nabout anime and manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Delicate Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.89,0:23:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-{\i1}kun{\i0}, the currents are \Nunstable, so I can't fly well!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
